org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel

Class HSSFPatriarch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFPatriarch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<HSSFShape>, HSSFShapeContainer, Drawing<HSSFShape>, ShapeContainer<HSSFShape> 

    public final class HSSFPatriarch
extends java.lang.Object
implements HSSFShapeContainer, Drawing<HSSFShape>
    The patriarch is the toplevel container for shapes in a sheet. It does little other than act as a container for other shapes and groups.(族长是薄片形状的顶层容器。它除了充当其他形状和群体的容器之外几乎没有什么作用。)

        Parameters:
